Soccer Boss: Player Module Readme
---------------------------------

The Player module defines the Player content type for the Soccer Boss
site. The Player Content type represents amateur soccer players and
includes links to important stats. The module also defines the Player
user role and its associated privileges. This role is granted to users
who want to track their personal development on the site.

Specifically, the Player module defines the following components:

  Content Types:
    1. Player
       Represents amateur soccer players.
  User Roles:
    1. Player
       Users who want to track their personal progress using the site.
